# INTERIOR::ACTIVATE_INTERIOR_ENTITY_SET

## Summary
Mark the entity set with the given name in this interior as being active

## Parameters
* **INTERIOR_INSTANCE_INDEX** interiorInstance
* **STRING** entitySetName
